        <div class="pf-why-item"><h3>Written Report for Warranty Protection</h3><p>The written report issued same day is your evidence that the system was properly maintained, essential for protecting a Worcester Bosch or Vaillant warranty worth thousands of pounds on a large Formby installation.</p></div>
